import os 
import re
<font face="Tahoma" size=5 color=#000000> Business Rating Trends in Arizona

<font face="Tahoma" size=3 color=#000000> In the first research question, we intend to investigate the Rating Trends of different businesses in Arizona to determine most promising businesses to invest in.
    
1. first rank businesses with amount and extract top 6 most popular businesses (shopping, restaurants, Home service, Nightlife, Fashion, Health Service)
2. merge the review dataset with business dataset based on businessID to find the corresponding business category of each review
3. transter date format to year, reviews are groupby year, obtain average rating each year for each category
4. Plot Business Rating Trend for Analysis

#  rank businesses with the amount to choose most popular businesses

cnt = corpus['categories'].value_counts().to_frame()[:20]

# choose different business categories
restarant_review_AZ =  review_data_AZ[review_data_AZ['categories'].str.contains('Restaurants')]  # restaurants

#beauty_review_AZ =  review_data_AZ[review_data_AZ['categories'].str.contains('Beauty')]  # beauty 
fashion_review_AZ =  review_data_AZ[review_data_AZ['categories'].str.contains('Fashion')]  # fashion

# change data formate to year

home_review_AZ['date'] =  pd.to_datetime(home_review_AZ['date'], format='%Y-%m').dt.year

plt.figure(figsize=(35, 15))

plt.xlabel('year',fontsize = 20)
plt.ylabel('stars(ratings)',fontsize = 20)

plt.title('rating trend of Health Services in AZ',fontsize = 20)
plt.xticks(fontsize=20)

plt.savefig(os.path.join('figures', 'business review trend_individual.png'), format='png', dpi=300)

# plot in the same graph
plt.figure(figsize=(35, 18))
sns.set(color_codes=True)
plt.plot(restarant_review_AZ_trend.index, restarant_review_AZ_trend['stars_x'], label='Restaurant',linewidth = 4)
plt.plot(shopping_review_AZ_trend.index, shopping_review_AZ_trend['stars_x'],label='Shopping',linewidth = 4)
plt.plot(home_review_AZ_trend.index, home_review_AZ_trend['stars_x'],label='Home Service',linewidth = 4)
plt.plot(night_review_AZ_trend.index, night_review_AZ_trend['stars_x'],label='Nightlife',linewidth = 4)
plt.plot(beauty_review_AZ_trend.index, beauty_review_AZ_trend['stars_x'],label='Fashion',linewidth = 4)
plt.plot(health_review_AZ_trend.index, health_review_AZ_trend['stars_x'],label='Health Service',linewidth = 4)
plt.xlabel('year',fontsize = 25)
plt.ylabel('stars(ratings)',fontsize = 25)
plt.legend(loc='lower right',fontsize = 25)
plt.xticks(fontsize=25)
plt.yticks(fontsize=25)
plt.title('Business Rating Trends in AZ',fontsize = 28 )
